---

---

<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-navy-950">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
          Not Another <span class="text-gradient">Agency</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          We don't plug in templates and walk away. We bring 8+ years of engineering discipline from building high-impact systems in Fintech and SaaS — and we apply that same rigor to your operations.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-400 shrink-0 mt-1"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-100">
                Reliability First
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">
                Your operations run on these systems. We build them to work in the background without constant hand-holding.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-400 shrink-0 mt-1"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-100">
                Data Security
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">
                Your data flows through these automations. We treat security as a core requirement, not an afterthought.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-400 shrink-0 mt-1"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-100">System Stability</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">
                We go beyond quick wins. Our systems are architected to scale and adapt as your business grows.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Background effects -->
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-600/10 to-electric-600/10 rounded-3xl blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class="relative bg-navy-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800/50 rounded-3xl p-8"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-6">
            Engineering Background
          </h3>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400 mb-2">8+</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Years in Fintech & SaaS</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-electric-400 mb-2">Product</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Engineering Focus</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400 mb-2">Custom</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Not Templates</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-electric-400 mb-2">Audit</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Before Action</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-800/50">
            <p class="text-center text-gray-400 italic">
              "I figure out where your team is wasting time on repetitive, low-value tasks — then build automated systems to handle them."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
